com.google.gxp.compiler.base
Interface Implementable

All Superinterfaces:
Callable, Serializable
public interface Implementable
extends Callable

Represents an interface created in gxp. Anything that is Implementable can only be called when you provide a concrete "this" instance. Any template that implements an Implementable should only require the parameters defined in the implementable.
